title: 820-00165 - does not recognize SSD
message:
There was oxidation on the U8070, I replaced it, but it still doesn't recognize it. The PP3V3_S0SW_SSD_FET_R with the SSD is 1.2v and without the SSD 2.4v. I've already changed it twice.

U8070
1 - 3.3v
2 - 3v
5 - 1.2v with SSD - 2.4v without SSD
7 -3.3v

U3740

8 - 0

No SSD

Any tips?

title: 820-00165 - does not recognize SSD
message:
Do you also have 3.3V at pin 3/U8070?
If yes, then bad chip; may also have bad solders.

title: 820-00165 - does not recognize SSD
message:
Yes, I have 3.3v pin 3.

I'll change it one more time. I've already tested with two.
